<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4786] [book] adding and reorganizing schema design information</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4786</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Adding more schema design information.  Consolidated the &quot;performance&quot; related schema options in the performance chapter so there wouldn&apos;t be explanations of these concepts in both the Schema Design chapter and also the Performance chapter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;book.xml&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;schema design chapter: moved the in-memory CF option, and bloom filter to the Peformance chapter&apos;s schema design section.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added link to performance chapter schema design section in Schema Design chapter.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added comment that online schema changes will be available in .92 (for an example where it shows a table being disabled for a CF change)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;performance.xml&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added the in-memory CF option and bloom filter reference from book.xml (see above)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added sub-section on per-table regionsize configuration.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added subsection on blocksize configuration.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;clarified entry on regionsizes and made it clear that large 20gb regions are only for HFile v2 format, whereas the largest HFile v1 format region is somewhere around 4gb.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
